###############################################################################
# Qwen Chat API - Testes de Rotas
#
# Para usar este arquivo:
#   - VS Code: instale a extensao "REST Client" (humao.rest-client)
#   - IntelliJ/WebStorm: suporte nativo a arquivos .http
#   - Clique em "Send Request" acima de cada requisicao
#
# Troque @baseUrl para apontar para seu ambiente:
#   - Local:      http://localhost:8080
###############################################################################

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080


###############################################################################
# 1. HEALTH CHECK
###############################################################################

### Verifica se o servidor esta no ar e testa o modelo
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

###############################################################################
# 2. FRONTEND
###############################################################################

### Carregar pagina principal (frontend HTML)
GET {{baseUrl}}/

###############################################################################
# 2. CHAT - Endpoint principal
###############################################################################

### Chat simples - mensagem basica
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Ola, quem e voce?"
}

### Chat com pergunta de conhecimento
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Qual a capital do Brasil?"
}

### Chat com historico (memoria de conversa)
# O modelo vai saber que "ela" se refere a "capital do Brasil"
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Qual a populacao dela?",
  "history": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "Qual a capital do Brasil?"},
    {"role": "assistant", "content": "A capital do Brasil e Brasilia."}
  ]
}

### Chat com session_id (salva conversa no servidor)
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Me explique o que e Docker em 3 linhas",
  "history": [],
  "session_id": "test-001"
}

### Chat que aciona a Tool de clima
# O modelo deve detectar a intencao e chamar [TOOL: clima_tempo]
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Como esta o clima em Sao Paulo agora?"
}

### Chat - Tool de clima com outra cidade
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Qual a temperatura em Tokyo?"
}

### Chat - Mensagem longa / criativa
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Escreva um poema curto sobre programacao"
}

###############################################################################
# 3. CHAT - Endpoints desabilitados (devem retornar 501)
###############################################################################

### Chat com imagem - DESABILITADO (espera 501)
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat/image
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="message"

Descreva esta imagem
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="test.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./static/index.html
--boundary--

### Chat com audio - DESABILITADO (espera 501)
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat/audio
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="audio"; filename="test.wav"
Content-Type: audio/wav

test
--boundary--

###############################################################################
# 4. CONFIGURACOES
###############################################################################

### Ver configuracoes atuais
GET {{baseUrl}}/config

### Alterar system prompt
POST {{baseUrl}}/config
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "system_prompt": "Voce e um assistente especializado em programacao Python. Responda sempre em portugues com exemplos de codigo."
}

### Alterar temperatura e max_tokens
POST {{baseUrl}}/config
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "temperature": 1.2,
  "max_tokens": 1024
}

### Alterar top_p
POST {{baseUrl}}/config
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "top_p": 0.95
}

### Alterar tudo de uma vez
POST {{baseUrl}}/config
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "system_prompt": "Voce e um assistente util e inteligente. Responda sempre em portugues.",
  "temperature": 0.7,
  "max_tokens": 512,
  "top_p": 0.9,
  "tools": [
    {
      "name": "clima_tempo",
      "description": "Consulta a previsao do tempo atual de qualquer cidade. Use quando o usuario perguntar sobre clima, tempo, temperatura ou previsao. Responda com [TOOL: clima_tempo] nome_da_cidade",
      "enabled": true
    }
  ]
}

### Desabilitar todas as tools
POST {{baseUrl}}/config
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tools": []
}

### Resetar config para valores padrao
POST {{baseUrl}}/config
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "system_prompt": "Voce e um assistente util e inteligente. Responda sempre em portugues.",
  "temperature": 0.7,
  "max_tokens": 512,
  "top_p": 0.9,
  "tools": [
    {
      "name": "clima_tempo",
      "description": "Consulta a previsao do tempo atual de qualquer cidade. Use quando o usuario perguntar sobre clima, tempo, temperatura ou previsao. Responda com [TOOL: clima_tempo] nome_da_cidade",
      "enabled": true
    }
  ]
}

###############################################################################
# 5. SESSOES DE CONVERSA
###############################################################################

### Listar todas as sessoes
GET {{baseUrl}}/sessions

### Criar nova sessao
POST {{baseUrl}}/sessions

### Ver detalhes de uma sessao (trocar o ID por um real)
GET {{baseUrl}}/sessions/test-001

### Enviar mensagem para uma sessao especifica
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Primeira mensagem desta sessao",
  "history": [],
  "session_id": "test-001"
}

### Ver sessao atualizada apos enviar mensagem
GET {{baseUrl}}/sessions/test-001

### Deletar uma sessao
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/sessions/test-001

### Confirmar que sessao foi deletada (deve retornar vazio)
GET {{baseUrl}}/sessions/test-001

###############################################################################
# 6. TESTES DE FLUXO COMPLETO
###############################################################################

### Fluxo 1: Criar sessao -> Enviar mensagem -> Ver historico -> Deletar

# Passo 1: Criar sessao (copie o ID retornado)
POST {{baseUrl}}/sessions

### Passo 2: Enviar mensagem (cole o ID da sessao)
# Troque "COLE_O_ID_AQUI" pelo ID retornado no passo 1
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Ola! Esta e uma sessao de teste.",
  "history": [],
  "session_id": "COLE_O_ID_AQUI"
}

### Passo 3: Ver historico da sessao
# Troque "COLE_O_ID_AQUI" pelo mesmo ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/sessions/COLE_O_ID_AQUI

### Passo 4: Deletar sessao
# Troque "COLE_O_ID_AQUI" pelo mesmo ID
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/sessions/COLE_O_ID_AQUI

###############################################################################
# 7. TESTE DE CARGA (envio rapido sequencial)
###############################################################################

### Pergunta 1
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Quanto e 2 + 2?"
}

### Pergunta 2
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Cite 3 linguagens de programacao"
}

### Pergunta 3
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "O que e uma API REST?"
}
